# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Ignore everything by default and re-include only needed files
**

# Re-include Go source files (but not *_test.go)
!**/*.go
**/*_test.go

# Re-include Go module files
!go.mod
!go.sum

# The non-production Hugging Face fixture embeds the project-owned GGUF corpus.
!internal/testfixtures/gguf/testdata/**

# Local toolchains and test caches may contain Go source but are never build input.
bin/
dist/

# The build embeds the release version into binaries and OCI labels.
!VERSION
